---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Service Level Agreement — Fimil"
  description="Fimil's uptime guarantees and support commitments."
>
  <article class="py-20 dark:bg-gray-950">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <a href="/legal" class="text-sm text-fimil-600 hover:text-fimil-700 dark:text-fimil-400"
        >&larr; Legal</a
      >
      <h1 class="mt-4 font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
        Service Level Agreement
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Effective Date: March 1, 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-8 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            1. Uptime Commitment
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Fimil targets 99.9% uptime for the SaaS platform, measured monthly. Scheduled
            maintenance windows are excluded.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            2. Support Response Times
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Critical issues: 4 hours. High: 8 hours. Medium: 24 hours. Low: 48 hours. Enterprise
            plans receive priority support.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            3. Service Credits
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            If monthly uptime falls below 99.9%, eligible customers receive service credits
            proportional to the downtime experienced.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            4. Exclusions
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Downtime caused by scheduled maintenance, force majeure, customer actions, or
            third-party services is excluded from SLA calculations.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            5. Contact
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            For SLA inquiries or to request service credits, contact <a
              href="mailto:support@fimil.dev"
              class="text-fimil-600 dark:text-fimil-400">support@fimil.dev</a
            >.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
